{"tid":652951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南澳洲百萬瓢蟲大軍壓境","createTime":"2018-05-04T09:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T10:54:09.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"73a5e445dda596ff92dad50b97326f4fbd27e695","tid":652951,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:11:50.000Z","msg":"密集恐懼慎CLICK<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205436535.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205436535.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8efce0bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205436535.jpg&h=68755a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205436535.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n在南澳洲一個偏遠小鎮近期出現一個熱門旅遊景點，哪裡沒有旖旎風光，也沒有動人鳥語花香，吸引無數遊客來「打卡」的是數以百萬計的瓢蟲。<br />\n據報道，每年同一時期，位於南澳甘比爾山（Mount Gambier）50公里外的小鎮伯爾山（Mount Burr）內，有一處遠程無線電塔都會被無以數計的瓢蟲佔領，場面蔚為壯觀。<br />\n澳洲居民Steve Chapple對此一直有著密切的關注，近年來還不斷近距離拍攝著這些迅速增長的昆蟲群，他表示：「我7年前開始記錄的時候，瓢蟲數量還很少，但現在已經要用百萬單位來計算它們。這是我見過最厚的瓢蟲群，覆蓋了5平方米，厚度達到了4英寸（約10厘米）。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205461257.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205461257.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b2708c2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205461257.jpg&h=0a0e5d3f\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205461257.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205549891.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205549891.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7c380d81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205549891.jpg&h=b619913a\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205549891.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n不過，Chapple也表示並非每一年都會有大量的瓢蟲來到此地：「它們通常在3月底開始出現，到5月底就都消失了。瓢蟲群不僅僅只聚集在一個地方，森林裡也到處都是。」<br />\n自從媒體報道過該地的瓢蟲聚集現像後，當地已成為熱門旅游景點，全球各地攝影師紛至沓來，拍攝這難得一見的瓢蟲群。<br />\n對此異象，阿德萊德大學教授Andy Austin解釋道，產生大量瓢蟲群的原因通常有很多：「兩個最為可能的原因是，牠們在交配期時會將同類都吸引到同個地方，基本上是為了更容易找到交配對像；第二個原因則可能是為了防止捕食者，尤其是鳥類。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205518729.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205518729.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=712e3bf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205518729.jpg&h=4f8fe70f\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205518729.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205686766.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205686766.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3786a39c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205686766.jpg&h=b956d9f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205686766.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205621897.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205621897.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c185c913\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205621897.jpg&h=9842b0d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205621897.jpg</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205790717.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205790717.jpg&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5235fada\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180504%2F_2018050416205790717.jpg&h=bf1beb08\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180504/_2018050416205790717.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/707585-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E5%AF%86%E9%9B%86%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC%E6%85%8E%E5%85%A5%21+%E5%8D%97%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E7%93%A2%E8%9F%B2%E5%A4%A7%E8%BB%8D%E5%A3%93%E5%A2%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F707585-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%25AF%2586%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2587%25BC%25E6%2585%258E%25E5%2585%25A5%2521%2B%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E7%2593%25A2%25E8%259F%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%25A2%2583&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=16a22b39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F707585-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E5%25AF%2586%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2